{"tid":689874,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"回復單身半年入紙結婚 「人渣」周永恒再婚娶大陸女友","createTime":"2018-06-04T11:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T09:33:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":220,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8fa5f8ee9ca37b28cf7755ed35ec65c9da2c00","tid":689874,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"自認「人渣」嘅34歲賤男周永恒（Roy），同前妻趙頌茹（阿Yu）育有兩女，但14年被爆背妻偷食劉依靜（Ruby），兩人嘅疑似淫照曝光，阿Yu更被家暴離家出走，兩人離婚收場。雖然Roy是非一籮籮，個底花喱花碌，估唔到依然有女埋身，上月底更入紙同32歲大陸女友陳薇結婚！<br />\n<br />\n對於前夫計劃再婚，阿Yu以短訊回覆《蘋果》：「無回應。」問到Roy有冇通知佢或囡囡再婚消息？阿Yu表示：「都係你哋問我先知。」問到幾時搞掂離婚手續？佢表示：「2017年年尾。」即係阿Roy回復單身未夠半年，已經急不及待申請再婚！問到Roy有冇探兩個囡囡？阿Yu同樣表示冇回應。<br />\n<br />\n而Roy另一位前度劉依靜（Ruby），當日疑介入Roy同阿Yu婚姻，近日風水輪流轉，傳被陳庭欣硬撬牆腳，搶走逾億彩豐行男友楊振源（Benny），Ruby對於舊愛Roy將再婚，同樣表示：「冇回應！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/194230_45577a88f0d19352c0d3cc270e898055.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F194230_45577a88f0d19352c0d3cc270e898055.png&h=3b35c14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180604/58276417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F58276417&d=kfJ6dqTQSMV4LBa3TGesqwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6c1da2a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F58276417&h=9a9ab5bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180604/58276417</a>"},{"pid":"72177f48ba71f0a88bd7ed299d606953063fae48","tid":689874,"uid":3109,"like":160,"dislike":3,"score":157,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"Ruby剩望樣都知係淫底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"